ADDITIONAL GRANT — Pledged Commons Tier

For use by any organization qualifying as a nonprofit, cooperative, academic
institution, or public-service entity (as evidenced by an IRS-verified EIN
under 501(c), or the international equivalent), Liana Banyan Corporation
grants the further right to use this software for its organizational purposes
under the terms of the Cooperative Defensive Patent Pledge, available at:

    https://liana-banyan.com/pledge

The Pledged Commons grant includes, in perpetuity:
  - Free use of the full feature set
  - No revocation based on organization size, output, or revenue
  - No patent sword from Liana Banyan Corporation against the organization
    for practice of the patented architecture covered by this software

The Pledged Commons grant is irrevocable by Liana Banyan Corporation except
in the case of demonstrated material breach of the Pledge itself.

