COMMERCIAL LICENSE

Organizations not qualifying for the Pledged Commons tier who wish to use
this software under terms other than AGPL-3.0 (including but not limited to
proprietary integration, closed-source distribution, or SaaS offerings that
would otherwise trigger AGPL §13 network-service requirements) may obtain
a commercial license by contacting enterprise@liana-banyan.com.

Commercial licenses are priced at Cost+20% of operating expense, consistent
with Liana Banyan Corporation's canonical margin philosophy. Commercial
licensees receive dedicated support, SLA, and contribute operationally to
the sustainability of the Pledged Commons tier.
